EN: He understood her plan clearly, and at the same time, he realized some issues.

ZH: 这篇文章的结论非常明了，而且是有根据的。
EN: The conclusion of this article is very clear and well-founded.

ZH: 他的演讲完全明了了争议的核心。
EN: His speech fully clarified the core of the controversy.

